text: Dasari Manohar Reddy is an Indian politician and member of the Telangana Legislative Assembly from the Peddapalli Constituency. He was first elected in 2014 then reelected in 2018. He was the founder of Trinity Educational Institution's. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Telangana MLAs 2014–2018 Category:Telangana MLAs 2018– Category:Telangana Rashtra Samithi politicians
